overview: The fourth volume of TransSensual's popular series features gorgeous and dominant TS ladies showing everyone who is boss!  Draven Navarro discovers the secret desires of his therapist, the gorgeous Melanie Brooks.  The amazing Natalie Mars takes her best friend Jenna Foxx on a secret vacation which brings them closer to each other.  When the stunning Khloe Kay moves in next door to Dante Colle, she introduces herself to the gorgeous man and they develop more than a neighborly relationship. Finally, Veronica (Jenna Gargles) and Gabbie (Haley Reed) find the house of their dreams. Unfortunately for them the house is not in their budget, but they decide to have a bit of fun with the cute real estate agent, Michael (Dante Colle).
title: TS Girls On Top 4
